OL,3,CLarge lorry fire closes busy
OL,4,CPortsmouth road
OL,6,FA large lorry fire has closed a major
OL,7,FPortsmouth road in both directions.
OL,9,FThe blaze broke out this afternoon
OL,10,F(Wednesday 8 April) along Eastern Road.
OL,12,FThe A2030 Eastern Road is blocked in
OL,13,Fboth directions with queueing traffic
OL,14,Ffrom Anchorage Road to Airport Service
OL,15,FRoad.
OL,17,FHampshire Fire and Rescue Service are
OL,18,Fwarning residents to keep windows and
OL,19,Fdoors closed due to the heavy smoke.
